Calm Animal or Plant

The most basic manifestation of a druid's connection with
Nature is the animal empathy many develop.  This ability
enables the druid to use that empathy to attempt to calm
an attacking animal.  It also works on plant-like
creatures, but not on humanoids or other beings.

Command: calm <target> (defaults to attacker)
Base Cost: 25 SP
Base Recovery: fast
Base Effect: stop fight
Base Duration: instant
Guild Level: 1
